}
```

## Notes
- The GLSL fragment shader performs up to 256 raymarch iterations — on low-end devices, reduce `volSteps` (default 110) or `dpr` to improve performance.
- Mouse interaction uses R3F's normalized `pointer` coordinates smoothed via `pointerSmoothing` lerp each frame.
